Ayyur n '''Ṛmḍan''' iga wayyur wiss tẓa ɣ uzwag anabawi, ar ittili dffir ayyur n Caɛban, iẓil wayyur ad dar imuslmn d imumnen acku nttan ad igan ayyur n wuẓum lli igan yan ɣ rrukn zɣ larkan n [[lislam]].

Issntay wayyur n Ṛmḍan kud-nna ẓṛṛin middn ayyur ɣ wass 29 n Caɛban, , iɣ ikmml rmḍan da sfuglan imuslmn s tfaslka n lfiṭr.

Dar wayyur n Ṛmḍan adɣar iẓlin ɣ taysi d umzruy n imuslmn, acku iggiz d gis adlis n rbbi [[Lqʷran|lquran]] zɣ llawḥ lmaḥfuḍ s ignna n ddunit ɣ yiḍ n lqadar ɣ wayyur ad, dffir iggizd ɣ-akud-ann imḍfrn ɣ uzmz n tuggza n lwaḥiy lliɣ illa urqqas [[Muḥammad]] taẓallit n rbbi fllas ɣ ifri n ḥira lliɣ yucka d dars lmalak jibril, inna as : اقْرَأْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الَّذِي خَلَقَ tga tkṭṭumt ad tamzwarut iggiz nn zɣ udlis n rbbi [[Lqʷran|lquran]].

Izdi wayyur n Ṛmḍan ɣ kigan n tmizar n lislam s agudi n inazwiyn n usgd zun d: taẓallit n ttarawiḥ d liɛtikaf ɣ timrawin tinggura, d tugt n tmyurin d ttaqalid zun d taɣuri i wiyyaḍ s lfḍur n [[Tiwwutci|tinwutci]].

